      "notes": [
        {
          "title": "byline",
          "text": "For the next set of problems, the reader is on his own until January [1984], when some help will be given.  Given the methods discussed here over the past year, the reader may be assured that at least some of them apply.  A device developed in a European country, apparently around the time of World War I, was used to encipher th problems, which are nevertheless in English."
        }
      ]
