      "notes": [
        {
          "title": "byline",
          "text": "Usually this column concludes with an explanation of the cipher system and the messages in the previous column.  This time will be an exception for the benefit of those readers who have not solved last issues messages as yet, but may lately have achieved an intuition.  For those readers who have solved the prior messages, I will add a few messages in basically the same system, perhaps with a simple change to make them somewhat harder."
        }
      ]
